{"text_id":103884,"tokens":["The"," first"," \"","welfare"," state","\""," was"," the"," United"," Kingdom",","," which"," introduced"," the"," Poor"," Law"," Amendment"," Act"," in"," ","1","8","3","4","."," The"," Act"," was"," passed"," in"," response"," to"," the"," high"," levels"," of"," poverty"," and"," homelessness"," in"," the"," country",","," and"," it"," aimed"," to"," provide"," relief"," for"," those"," in"," need","."," The"," Act"," was"," a"," major"," turning"," point"," in"," the"," history"," of"," social"," welfare"," in"," the"," UK",","," and"," it"," laid"," the"," foundations"," for"," the"," modern"," welfare"," state",".","\n\n","The"," Poor"," Law"," Amendment"," Act"," was"," based"," on"," the"," idea"," that"," poverty"," was"," a"," problem"," that"," could"," be"," solved"," through"," the"," provision"," of"," relief","."," The"," Act"," introduced"," a"," system"," of"," work","houses",","," which"," were"," designed"," to"," provide"," accommodation"," and"," food"," for"," those"," in"," need","."," The"," work","houses"," were"," intended"," to"," be"," a"," last"," resort"," for"," those"," who"," were"," unable"," to"," support"," themselves",","," and"," they"," were"," often"," criticized"," for"," their"," harsh"," conditions"," and"," the"," way"," they"," treated"," their"," residents",".","\n\n","Despite"," these"," criticisms",","," the"," Poor"," Law"," Amendment"," Act"," was"," a"," significant"," step"," forward"," in"," the"," history"," of"," social"," welfare"," in"," the"," UK","."," It"," provided"," a"," system"," of"," relief"," for"," those"," in"," need",","," and"," it"," laid"," the"," foundations"," for"," the"," modern"," welfare"," state","."," The"," Act"," was"," a"," precursor"," to"," the"," Social"," Security"," Act"," of"," ","1","9","7","5",","," which"," introduced"," the"," modern"," welfare"," state"," in"," the"," UK",".","\n\n","The"," modern"," welfare"," state"," is"," a"," system"," of"," social"," welfare"," that"," provides"," a"," range"," of"," benefits"," and"," services"," to"," those"," in"," need","."," The"," benefits"," and"," services"," provided"," by"," the"," welfare"," state"," include"," unemployment"," benefits",","," sick"," benefits",","," and"," pensions","."," The"," welfare"," state"," also"," provides"," a"," range"," of"," services",","," such"," as"," education",","," healthcare",","," and"," housing",".","\n\n","The"," welfare"," state"," is"," a"," major"," component"," of"," the"," modern"," social"," safety"," net",","," and"," it"," plays"," a"," vital"," role"," in"," providing"," support"," for"," those"," in"," need","."," The"," welfare"," state"," is"," often"," criticized"," for"," its"," inefficiency"," and"," its"," tendency"," to"," encourage"," dependency",","," but"," it"," is"," also"," widely"," praised"," for"," its"," role"," in"," providing"," support"," for"," those"," who"," are"," unable"," to"," support"," themselves",".","\n\n","The"," welfare"," state"," has"," evolved"," over"," time",","," and"," it"," has"," been"," subject"," to"," a"," range"," of"," reforms"," and"," changes","."," The"," most"," significant"," change"," to"," the"," welfare"," state"," in"," recent"," years"," has"," been"," the"," introduction"," of"," the"," Universal"," Credit"," system",","," which"," is"," intended"," to"," simplify"," the"," system"," of"," benefits"," and"," make"," it"," more"," effective",".","\n\n","The"," Universal"," Credit"," system"," is"," a"," major"," reform"," of"," the"," welfare"," state",","," and"," it"," has"," been"," subject"," to"," a"," range"," of"," criticisms"," and"," controversies","."," The"," system"," has"," been"," criticized"," for"," its"," complexity"," and"," its"," lack"," of"," support"," for"," those"," who"," are"," unable"," to"," navigate"," it","."," The"," system"," has"," also"," been"," criticized"," for"," its"," tendency"," to"," cause"," hardship"," for"," those"," who"," are"," already"," struggling"," to"," make"," ends"," meet",".","\n\n","Despite"," these"," criticisms",","," the"," Universal"," Credit"," system"," is"," a"," significant"," step"," forward"," in"," the"," history"," of"," the"," welfare"," state","."," It"," is"," a"," more"," streamlined"," and"," efficient"," system"," of"," benefits",","," and"," it"," is"," intended"," to"," provide"," a"," more"," effective"," safety"," net"," for"," those"," in"," need","."," The"," system"," is"," a"," work"," in"," progress",","," and"," it"," is"," likely"," to"," be"," subject"," to"," further"," reforms"," and"," changes"," in"," the"," future","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"cohere","label":1}